<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c1bbae19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n可以去task1入面美國參議員講香港的tweets Reply講星火被凍結資產的事件<br />\n<br />\n記住twitter一定要用reply ，令外國議員見到香港最新狀況/外國媒體報導，先係衝到出國際，如果只係香港人出tweet，大家香港人不斷rt, 都剩係停留響同溫層本地圍爐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線:要令星火事件上到國際！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789690</a>"},{"pid":"868cdd09831df9d556b2f6278fb6624d8bd9bcba","tid":1789753,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"芝牛丼LL"},{"pid":"ff1ccefc9fa83d003390a0c40c4da3d4c6400e25","tid":1789753,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:41:10.000Z","msg":"蛋牛飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729db2af4bf7ee29fe1467eaa1b1c7470206601c","tid":1789753,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:46:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港由港足做起<br />\n<br />\nWe are Hong Kong 🇭🇰🇭🇰🇭🇰<br />\nOle ole ole<br />\n<br />\n本谷旨在想有興趣睇港足港超或者一路有睇開的球迷入嚟一齊討論傾下波經。以老帶新，由資深球迷帶新手球迷入門，交換資訊，降低香港睇波門檻，等愈來愈多球迷入場撐港足，重建香港球巿。<br />\n<br />\n入group嘅可以講低自己中意邊隊，得閒約埋一齊去睇波。仲等咩快d入嚟<br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=9a8db6d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a>"},{"pid":"7cf52b6d7e1e1d2b12bd157bada0dc5b86e7247b","tid":1789753,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"868cdd09831df9d556b2f6278fb6624d8bd9bcba","tid":1789753,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:34:20.000Z"